	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Really shouldn't have used JPEGs.  Please use PNGs for such screenshots/captures.  JPEGs are lossy (I can see the compression and it makes distinguishing visual artefacts from video noise/etc. very difficult), while PNGs are not lossy.  Thanks.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


